<QuestionForm xmlns="http://mechanicalturk.amazonaws.com/AWSMechanicalTurkDataSchemas/2017-11-06/QuestionForm.xsd">
  <Overview>
    <Title>20 Questions Qualification</Title>
    <Text>
      We're looking for people to play 20 Questions so that we can gather
      common sense facts. This qualification allows you to play the
      games, and will test your understanding of the kinds of data we're
      looking for.

      When running the HITs, we'll send out an email beforehand with the
      time and title for the HITs we'll post, and then people can show
      up and play the games at that time.
    </Text>
  </Overview>
  <Overview>
    <FormattedContent>
      <![CDATA[
        To start a round of 20 Questions, you'll have to choose a
        <i>subject</i>. It should be an object or thing that the other
        players will know well and <b>not</b> the name of something
        specific or another kind of unique thing.
      ]]>
    </FormattedContent>
    <FormattedContent>
      <![CDATA[
        <b>Good</b> Examples:
      ]]>
    </FormattedContent>
    <List>
      <ListItem>chair</ListItem>
      <ListItem>air</ListItem>
      <ListItem>time</ListItem>
    </List>
    <FormattedContent>
      <![CDATA[
        <b>Bad</b> Examples:
      ]]>
    </FormattedContent>
    <List>
      <ListItem>Barack Obama</ListItem>
      <ListItem>2018</ListItem>
      <ListItem>The Titanic</ListItem>
    </List>
  </Overview>
